177
00:08:30,910 --> 00:08:32,030
M-My stomach...

178
00:08:32,049 --> 00:08:32,610
Sit down.

179
00:08:36,510 --> 00:08:38,309
Let's get straight to the point.

180
00:08:39,049 --> 00:08:39,980
I want to talk to you

181
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:42,309
